title: #92Noon! Russo fills in for PA!
description: Russo brings a hockey-heavy show to #92Noon. Opens with Wild GK Alex Stalock, Jon Krawczynski in studio, emergency GK Connor Beaupre, Anthony Lapanta in studio for full hour, Mike Zimmer presser, & hockey insider Pierre LeBrun!
